                    <cite class="fn">rich</cite>
                    <span class="comment-meta">
                        <a class="rtp-common-link rtp-comment-date" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/12/04/gold-smuggling-increases-7x-in-india-and-surpasses-illegal-drug-trade/#comment-18039" title="December 4, 2013">
